All Implemented Interfaces:
com.icesoft.faces.component.IceExtended, javax.faces.component.EditableValueHolder, javax.faces.component.StateHolder, javax.faces.component.ValueHolder
public class HtmlSelectManyCheckbox
extends javax.faces.component.html.HtmlSelectManyCheckbox
implements com.icesoft.faces.component.IceExtended

This is an extension of javax.faces.component.html.HtmlSelectManyCheckbox, which provides some additional behavior to this component such as:

  • default classes for enabled and disabled state
  • provides partial submit mechanism
  • changes the component's enabled and rendered state based on the authentication
  • adds effects to the component
